subject: Basketball
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Tim Abromaitis had 25 points, Tyrone Nash scored 18 and Notre Dame rallied from 12 points down at halftime for an 89-83 victory over Georgia.
